如果只看单个光粒子，很多现象根本讲不通。
单个粒子只是独立运动，很难去解释间距、排布、整体偏移，还有有规律的明暗纹路。
单独粒子没法说明：
为什么会有群体的规律分布，
为什么经过缝隙、圆孔边缘会产生大范围扩散和有序纹路。
所以必须把能量包当成单个完整实体来看待。
能量包是大量粒子聚集在一起的整体单元。
不管是单独分散的粒子，还是拼排聚集在一起的粒子，
遇到边界都会发生偏移。
有了能量包这个实体单位：
能说清粒子之间的距离、排列结构；
能解释边缘挤压、限位、整体偏转；
双缝往两侧扩散、圆孔向四周全方位扩散，两种机制都能统一说明；
不用借用波动、虚假抵消那一套，只用实体运动、实体排布，就能全部自洽。
简单讲：
只靠单个粒子，逻辑有断层、想象不出来；
加上独立实体化的能量包，整套理论才通顺、能预测、能对应所有光学实验。
Why It Is Necessary to Establish the Concept of Energy Packets
If we only look at individual light particles, many phenomena cannot be explained at all.
A single particle only moves independently, making it difficult to explain the spacing, arrangement, overall deviation, and regular light and dark patterns.
Individual particles cannot explain:
why there is a regular group distribution,
and why large-scale diffusion and ordered patterns are generated when passing through the edges of slits or circular holes.
Therefore, energy packets must be regarded as single complete entities.
An energy packet is an integral unit composed of a large number of aggregated particles.
Whether they are individual scattered particles or aggregated and arranged particles,
they will all deviate when encountering a boundary.
With the entity unit of energy packets:
It can clarify the distance between particles and their arrangement structure;
It can explain edge extrusion, position limitation, and overall deflection;
It can uniformly explain the two mechanisms: lateral diffusion through double slits and all-round radial diffusion through circular holes;
There is no need to resort to the false theories of waves and false cancellation—all phenomena can be self-consistent only by using physical motion and physical arrangement.
